  <rdf:Description rdf:about="http://publications.europa.eu/resource/pegase/143605.320672">
    <j.0:comment xml:lang="fr">The European Parliament at its Second Reading adopted 17 amendments. Parliament mainly aims to make the target values and long term objectives on ozone more binding and to introduce a fixed target year by which the long term objectives must be met.</j.0:comment>
    <j.0:event_legal_comment xml:lang="fr">The European Parliament at its Second Reading adopted 17 amendments. Parliament mainly aims to make the target values and long term objectives on ozone more binding and to introduce a fixed target year by which the long term objectives must be met.</j.0:event_legal_comment>
